        ]
      },
      "text": [
        " اللَّهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ وَ الَّذِينَ لا يَشْهَدُونَ الزُّورَ قَالَ هُوَ الْغِنَاءُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Abu Ayoub, from Muhammad Bin Muslim, and Abu Al Sabbah Al Kinany, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> regarding the Words of Allah<sup>azwj</sup> Mighty and Majestic <span class=\"ibTxt\"><a href=\"/#/books/quran:25#h72\"><a href=\"/#/books/quran:25#h72\">[25:72]</a></a> And they who are not witnessing (attending) what is false</span>. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘It is the singing (music)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "13. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from abu Ayyub from Muhammad ibn Muslim and abu ai-Sabbah af-Kinaniy who has said the following: “About the meaning of the words of Allah, most Majestic, most Glorious, ‘. . . those who do not attend al-Zur . . .’ <a href=\"/#/books/quran:25#h72\"><a href=\"/#/books/quran:25#h72\">[25:72]</a></a> abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘It is music (and singing).”’ "
        ]
      }
    }
